        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "6PC KITCHEN UTENSILS SET - Do some of your old kitchen utensils need an upgrade? Why not make it a sustainable one? 6pc set comes with an ice cream scoop, cheese grater, vegetable peeler, pizza cutter, measuring cups, and measuring spoons, all made from wheat straw in a modern and fresh cream-speckled matte finish",
