        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Is your kitchen utensil drawer in need of an overhaul or upgrade? Why not make it a sustainable one? <br/>Look no further than Beille’s wheat straw kitchen gadgets 6pc set, all made from bioplastic wheat straw:<br/><br/>-5-piece measuring spoon set<br/>-5-piece measuring cup set<br/>-Ice cream scooper<br/>-Y peeler<br/>-Pizza cutter<br/>-Cheese grater<br/><br/>The kitchen utensils all feature thick, rounded handles with a speckled matte finish, ensuring a comfortable and controlled grip for all your meal prep tasks. And, notably, the pizza cutter wheel, vegetable peeler or Y peeler, and cheese grater all feature a built-in handle hole, allowing for hanging over the drawer or cupboard storage if preferred.<br/><br/>As mentioned, all the kitchen utensils included in this bundle are made from bioplastic wheat straw, an alternative plant-based material to other less forgiving solid plastics; renewable and sustainable, the kitchen utensils are food safe and certified BPA Free. Beille’s wheat straw kitchen tools mimic traditional plastic kitchen utensils' functionality without harmful byproducts. These kitchen gadgets are dishwasher safe, making for a quick and easy clean-up.<br/><br/>No kitchen is complete without these kitchen utensils. Must have kitchen tools, upgrade your current knives to a sustainable one, or gift them as a hostess or housewarming gift alongside other items from Beille’s wheat straw kitchen collection.",
